Class FinancialInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.oakland.finaid.mvc.models.FinancialInfo

  • public class FinancialInfo
extends java.lang.Object
    Holds the user's financial information. It's a data model that itself contains the data models for academic awards, holds, and progress.

    1.0
